      <h3><span class="field-group-format-toggler">Process</span></h3>
      <div class="field-group-format-wrapper" style="display: block;"><div class="field field-name-field-methods field-type-node-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Methods:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/methods/collaborative-governance">Collaborative Governance</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/methods/participatory-budgeting">Participatory Budgeting</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/methods/public-hearing">Public Hearing</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-facilitated field-type-list-boolean field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Facilitation?:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Yes</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-facilitation-type field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">If yes, were they ...:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_facilitation_type%3A170">Professional Facilitators</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-facilitation-method field-type-list-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Facetoface, Online or Both:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Face-to-Face</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-communication-mode field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Type of Interaction among Participants:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_communication_mode%3A9">Discussion, Dialogue, or Deliberation</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-decision-method field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Decision Method(s)?:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_decision_method%3A144">Opinion Survey</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-decision-voting-type field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">If voting...:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">[no data entered]</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-targeted-audience field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Targeted Audience :&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_targeted_audience%3A151">General Public</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_targeted_audience%3A152">Elected Public Official</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-audience-comm-method field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Method of Communication with Audience:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_audience_comm_method%3A158">Policy Recommendations</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_audience_comm_method%3A159">Public Hearings/Meetings</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="collapsible group-organizers field-group-div speed-fast effect-none">
      <h3><span class="field-group-format-toggler">Organizers</span></h3>
      <div class="field-group-format-wrapper" style="display: block;"><div class="field field-name-field-funded-by field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Who paid for the project or initiative?:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Government of Kerala</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-funding-entity-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Type of Funding Entity:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_funding_entity_kind%3A25">Regional Government (e.g. State, Provincial, Territorial)</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-sponsoring-organization field-type-node-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Who was primarily responsible for organizing the initiative?:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">[no data entered]</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-implementing-entity-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Type of Organizing Entity:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_implementing_entity_kind%3A25">Regional Government (e.g. State, Provincial, Territorial)</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_implementing_entity_kind%3A19">Local Government (e.g. Village, Town, City)</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-initiative-support-other field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Who else supported the initiative? :&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">[no data entered]</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-sponsoring-entity-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Types of Supporting Entities:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_sponsoring_entity_kind%3A25">Regional Government (e.g. State, Provincial, Territorial)</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_sponsoring_entity_kind%3A19">Local Government (e.g. Village, Town, City)</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="collapsible group-resources field-group-div speed-fast effect-none">
      <h3><span class="field-group-format-toggler">Resources</span></h3>
      <div class="field-group-format-wrapper" style="display: block;"><div class="field field-name-field-case-budget field-type-number-decimal field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Total Budget:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">[no data entered]</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-case-budget-annual field-type-number-decimal field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Average Annual Budget:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">[no data entered]</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-staff-full-time field-type-number-integer field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Number of Full-Time Staff:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">[no data entered]</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-staff-part-time field-type-number-integer field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Number of Part-Time Staff:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">[no data entered]</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-staff-type field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Staff Type:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Government Officials</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-volunteers field-type-number-integer field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Number of Volunteers:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">[no data entered]</div></div></div></div></div></div></div>      </div>
